              "text": " — a per-site "
            },
            {
              "text": "trust switch",
              "marks": ["highlight"]
            },
            {
              "text": " (Settings → Privacy) lets login-gated sites like x.com work normally, while every other site keeps the strict tracker- and cookie-blocking default."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "h1",
          "text": "Fixes"
        },
        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Appearance",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
