    {
      "version": "0.3.0",
      "date": "2026-07-10",
      "icon": "🔒",
      "title": "Removing someone really removes them",
      "summary": "When you take a collaborator off a shared note, page, or channel, they can no longer read anything you write afterward — access removal is now enforced by encryption, not just policy. Plus a PDF crash fix.",
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "h1",
          "text": "Forward-secret revocation"
        },
        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Sharing",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
            {
              "text": " — when you "
            },
            {
              "text": "remove someone",
              "marks": ["highlight"]
            },
            {
              "text": " from a shared item, its encryption key is rotated and re-sealed for the people who remain. The removed person is left holding only the old key, so every edit you make "
            },
            {
              "text": "after",
              "marks": ["highlight"]
            },
            {
              "text": " they're removed is unreadable to them — even if their app is still connected."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Works offline",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
            {
              "text": " — remove someone while you're offline and the key rotation is queued, then completes automatically the moment you reconnect."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "callout",
          "icon": "🕰️",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "What they already saw, they keep. ",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
            {
              "text": "Like every honest end-to-end encrypted system, removal is forward-looking: it stops future access — it can't un-send what already synced to their device."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "h1",
          "text": "Fixes"
        },
        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Preview",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
            {
              "text": " — opening and closing certain "
            },
            {
              "text": "PDFs",
              "marks": ["highlight"]
            },
            {
              "text": " no longer crashes the app."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "callout",
          "icon": "🔄",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Update in place. ",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
            {
              "text": "Existing installs update from "
            },
            {
              "text": "Settings → Updates",
              "marks": ["highlight"]
            },
            {
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
