      "date": "2026-07-07",
      "icon": "🔔",
      "title": "Reminders you can rely on",
      "summary": "A quality release: task and calendar reminders now fire even when the app is closed, duplicate alerts are gone, synced attachments can be cleaned up server-side, and every known dependency vulnerability is patched.",
      "body": [
        {
          "kind": "h1",
          "text": "Reminders"
        },
        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Tasks",
