        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": "Opening the app no longer risks a duplicate — the shell and the app coordinate so each alert appears exactly once."
        },
        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": "Alerts respect Do Not Disturb and per-app mutes, and land in the notification center like everything else."
        },
        {
          "kind": "h1",
          "text": "Under the hood"
