        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Sync",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
            {
              "text": " — your devices now report which encrypted attachments they still use, so the sync node can safely reclaim storage from deleted files. Reclamation stays conservative: anything a recently-seen device references is kept."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "kind": "li",
          "text": [
            {
              "text": "Security",
              "marks": ["bold"]
            },
            {
              "text": " — all 69 known dependency vulnerabilities patched, including the mail sender and the spreadsheet preview parser; the build toolchain moved to current majors."
            }
